FlowCandy is the only full service Retention Marketing Agency. 

Our team of experts has helped hundreds of stores grow their LTV and profit by helping them strategize (and implement!) growth tactics on channels such as email, sms, subscriptions, loyalty, reviews, upsells, and more!

We're totally turnkey and can do everything it takes to launch successful email automations and campaigns, such as: 

// All copywriting
// All template designs and tweaks
// Build new flows
// Launch new campaigns/newsletters
// All reporting & analytics
// All support
// Plus much more!

Our team has worked with over 100+ stores and have driven millions of dollars in email marketing revenue.  We're also changing the way stores can scale their email marketing with a new offer that allows you to launch or edit unlimited emails, flows, drips and popups... without hiring a freelancer.

Sway is a leading social-first digital agency and Emmy-winning production studio with capabilities across owned, paid and earned media. | #SwayThem

// INFLUENCER NETWORK

From Grammy-nominated artists to YouTube's #1 Beauty & Style channel and Snapchat's biggest names our creators provide original scalable content creation and direct-to-consumer distribution to brands and agencies worldwide.

